Start doing these⬇️

SAVE for later

1️⃣Lift heavier weights, not just light dumbbells - Muscle loss starts in your 30s. Train like you’re preventing it.

2️⃣Eat 20-30g of protein per meal - Not just for fitness goals, but to keep your metabolism and hormones in check.

3️⃣Stop over-exfoliating your skin - Your
skin barrier will hate you later if you destroy it with scrubs and actives now.

4️⃣Stop ignoring the 10,000 steps rule - No, your gym session doesn’t cancel out a sedentary lifestyle. Move more.

5️⃣Drink water before coffee - Your adrenals will thank you. Caffeine on an empty stomach spikes stress hormones.

6️⃣Fix your tech neck - Constantly
looking down at your phone = early
wrinkles and chronic neck pain.

7️⃣Cycle-sync your workouts and diet - 
Your body’s needs change throughout your cycle! train and eat accordingly. 

8️⃣Get bloodwork done yearly - Don’t guess when it comes to hormones, vitamins, and inflammation levels.

#tips #health #wellness #holistic #advice #aging
